<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hang takin Van sepaihte haw,
 Lauh umna ah chieh zel unla;
 Isu I Puipau ahi a,
 Kalvari achun A zo tai;

[V2]
 I Lalpau ei Puipa'n.
 I Lalpau ei Puipa'n (3)
 Gam nuom ei tun ina (4)
 I Lalpau ei Puipa'n.

[V3]
 2. Hang takin van sepaihte haw,
 Thih leh natah chiehpai unla;
 Isu I Puipau ahi a,
 Thana patin A thokit tai;
 I Lalpau ei Puipa.

[V4]
 3. Hang takin Van sepaihte haw,
 Aksi khel gama chieh hitiu;
 Isu I Puipau ahi a,
 A van In nuom tung ngei hitiu;
 I Lalpau ei Puipa.</lyrics>
<title>JESUS LEADS US</title>
</song>